short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Replaces the new tab with a custom page displaying live data.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Stay updated with the latest information about the people currently in space every time you open a new tab. Space Population Live provides real-time data on the number of astronauts, their names, and the spacecraft they are on.

Features:

- Live Space Population Count: See the current number of people in space every time you open a new tab.
- Astronaut Details: View the names of all astronauts and their respective spacecraft, such as the International Space Station (ISS) and Tiangong.
- Clean and Simple Design: Enjoy a user-friendly interface that integrates seamlessly with your new tab page.
- Real-Time Updates: Data is fetched in real-time using the Open Notify API to ensure you always have the latest information.

Watch the number of people in space grow!
